## Sample Document

`data/company_policy.txt` — ACME Corporation Employee Policy Handbook

| Section | Topic |
|---------|-------|
| 1 | Leave Policy (annual, sick, maternity, emergency) |
| 2 | Work Hours & Remote Work |
| 3 | Code of Conduct |
| 4 | Compensation & Benefits |
| 5 | Performance & Appraisal |
| 6 | Grievance & Disciplinary Process |
| 7 | IT & Data Security |

### Sample queries & expected answers

| Query | Expected Answer |
|-------|----------------|
| How many paid leave days per year? | 20 days annually |
| What is the weekend overtime rate? | 2× hourly rate |
| How many WFH days are allowed? | Up to 2 days per week |
| When are salaries credited? | Last working day of each month |
| What is the password expiry period? | Every 90 days |

